<H3> <TI>   Dutch Prime Minister Arrives on Official Visit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Dutch Prime Minister Arrives on Official Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1904172194 Bucharest ROMPRES in English 1420 GMT 19 Apr 94 
